523
00:44:38,080 --> 00:44:40,089
Ooohh!

524
00:44:40,800 --> 00:44:42,445
You're a couple of turds.

525
00:44:50,560 --> 00:44:52,679
Listen, asshole...

526
00:44:52,680 --> 00:44:56,559
little piece of turd,
you're nobody to us.

