lock themselves in
their room, you know?

551
00:46:43,720 --> 00:46:46,799
Cut their hair,
paint it red, you know?

552
00:46:46,800 --> 00:46:49,207
Put wigs on and shit like that?

553
00:46:50,160 --> 00:46:51,600
No. Never.

554
00:46:52,960 --> 00:46:55,559
I knew it! I'm in trouble.

