641
00:52:36,920 --> 00:52:40,090
That's OK, honey. I'm sorry, too.

642
00:52:41,160 --> 00:52:43,479
Favorite place to hang
out after school?

643
00:52:45,560 --> 00:52:49,845
I'll wrap my sales meeting and
meet you at 3:30, sweetie.

