What do you think about that?

645
00:52:55,880 --> 00:52:58,799
A girl like this will keep
you running in circles.

646
00:52:58,800 --> 00:53:02,083
You must draw the
line, not be so soft.

647
00:53:04,640 --> 00:53:06,569
You're right, Mitat.

648
00:53:08,440 --> 00:53:10,199
